			<note xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" place="foot" n="9" xml:id="foot_7"><p>Results for SUMRDF on YAGO and Wikidata could not be reported, as the summary building for that graph did not finish after 12 hours.</p></note>
			<note xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" place="foot" n="10" xml:id="foot_8"><p>Please note that this is not a problem of the query generator, but rather that KGs in general exhibit a small diameter<ref type="bibr" target="#b53">Zloch et al. [2019]</ref>, which makes the number of different path queries considerable smaller than the number of star queries.</p></note>
